data.text:
Sub-project of WikiProject Iowa

This is the government section for WikiProject Iowa. Its scope includes those articles which are part of WikiProject Iowa and which are related to government (e.g. Iowa General Assembly, Steve Warnstadt, Code of Iowa, United States Congressional Delegations from Iowa). If you tag an article as part of this section please add them to one or more of the tables in the "Assessment" section below.

Any article on an Iowa politician will fall under WikiProject Iowa. Use the following in the template:

{{WikiProject United States|class=|importance=|IA=yes|IA-importance=|listas=}}

Information about every current federal and state level politician can be found at Project Vote Smart, though as of October 2011 , it appears that pages disappear when the politician is no longer in office.

A biography of every U.S. Senator and Representative can be found at this public domain source: http://bioguide.congress.gov/biosearch/biosearch.asp

Information about every U.S. federal judge can be found at this public domain source: http://air.fjc.gov/history/home.nsf/Judges!OpenFrameSet

Information about past and present Iowa State Senators and Representatives can be found at the Iowa General Assembly website

The biannually published Iowa Official Register (Redbook) is a good source of information on members of the Iowa executive, legislative, and judicial branches. Many editions also contain election results, historical and governmental essays, and useful photos or portraits. Older editions are at commons:Category:Iowa Official Register, virtually all editions are on the Iowa legislature's website.

Information about members, and other information about the Iowa General Assembly from 1981-2002 can be found here, in a supplement to The Iowa General Assembly: Our Legislative Heritage 1846-1980, complied by Francis (Frank) J. Stork and Cynthia A. Clingan and published in 1979).

Iowa biographies can be found in History of Iowa From the Earliest Times to the Beginning of the Twentieth Century - Volume 4
